Package moblima.entity

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Booking
    Represents a booking record.
    Cinema
    Represents a cinema in the cineplex Contains information of class of this cinema and cinema code of this cinema and seats in this cinema and cinema index of this cinema and number of empty seats in this cinema and number of rows of seats in this cinema and number of columes of seats in this cinema cinema can show different movies
    Cineplex
    Represents a Cineplex organized by MOBLIMA system Contains name of cineplex and a list of cinemas in this Cineplex
    MovieInfo
    Represents information of a movie Contains title, showing status, type, synopsis, directors, a list of casts, overallRating, a list of past reviews, base ticket price, rating, and sale about this movie
    MovieShowing
    Represents a movie which is showing in a cinema Contains the intruduction information about this movie, the cinema where the movie is showing at, the cineplex where the movie is showing at and the show time when the movie is showing
    MovieTicket
    Represents information on a movie ticket Contains the movie, seat and price of this ticket
    Payment
    Represents a payment during movie ticket booking Payment contains the information of transactionID, name, mobile number and email of payer, and amount of this payment
    Review
    Represents a Review for the movie Contains the comment content and rating of the Review
    Seat
    Represents a Seat in the cinema Contains information of seat ID and its status
    User
    Represent a user who is using MOBLIMA Including STAFF and MOVIEGOER
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Cinema.ClassOfCinema
    Enumeration for class of cinema Including GOLD, MAX and NORMAL
    MovieInfo.Rating
    Enumeration for ratings of movie Including G, PG, PG13, NC16, M18 and R21
    MovieInfo.ShowingStatus
    Enumeration for showing statuses of movie Including COMINGSOON, PREVIEW, NOWSHOWING and ENDOFSHOWING
    MovieInfo.TypeOfMovie
    Enumeration for types of movie Including 3D and BLOCKBUSTER
    Seat.enumSeat
    Enumeration for statuses of Seat Including NOTEXIST, TAKEN and NOTTAKEN
    User.TypeOfUser
    Enumeration for type of users Including STAFF and MOVIEGOER
